@startuml svc-trail-management--patch-trails-trail_id

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #7c3aed
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
    BoxBorderColor #94A3B8
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
    NoteBorderColor #64748B
    NoteBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

header [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#integration-context ⬆ svc-trail-management Integration Context]]

title PATCH /trails/{trail_id}\nUpdate trail details

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-trail-management" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/]] #FEF3C7
database "PostGIS" as DB [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-trail-management.html#/Trails/updateTrail View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : PATCH /trails/{trail_id}
activate GW #7c3aed
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #7c3aed

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : SELECT ... FOR UPDATE
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Current row
deactivate DB
note right of Svc : Merge changed fields only

Svc -> DB : UPDATE ... SET ...
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Updated row
deactivate DB

Svc --> GW : 200 OK
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 200 OK
deactivate GW

@enduml